			red V spawns in the room next to the three caster trainers, he spawns about once every sixth minute, he is lvl 4-6, he drops an incomplete blackbox wich you have to fill with four blackbox fragments (wich are found on obsolete models and runaway clockworks) and combine, give it to Manik Compolten in the warriors guild. You dont have to get the quest from him just give him the box. I have almost every time gotten PW and Raw-hide armor and small wooden shields. Rarely you get the Bull smasher 1h blunt small races only dmg 6 atk 20 +2 str, +2agi and +2dex.<BR>
